USEFUL FUNCTIONS & DESCRIPTIONS ETC USED IN CHAP1 AND CHAP2

CHAP1
  typeof() - return type of argument
  round() - round to given number of dec. places
  ls() (list variables)
  args(function name) - gives list of arguments

Arithmetic for ordinary numbers but which can be used on vectors
  + - * / **(power)
  round()
  
  For vectors
  c(.....)
  %*% = innner multiplcation
  %o% = outer multiplication


Stats etc
  mean(<vector>)
  sample(vector, size, replace = TRUE) (otherwise replace = FALSE)
  
  sort(<vector>) ... useful other than in stats



